        {
            "title": "美國加大施壓 澤連斯基提出由公投決定頓巴斯的前途",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 面對美國施壓基輔接受和平方案的力度越來越大，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:烏克蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/烏克蘭\">烏克蘭</a>總統沃洛迪米爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>拋出了通過公投來決定東部領土命運的想法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">莫斯科堅持要求烏克蘭從該國東部的頓巴斯撤軍，儘管俄軍在近四年的入侵中一直未能全部控制這個由頓涅茨克和盧甘斯克組成的地區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基已親自就美國政府提出的最新和平方案參與談判，但他仍然堅持烏克蘭不會考慮向俄羅斯割讓領土的立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「俄國人想要整個頓巴斯，我們不接受，」 澤連斯基周四在基輔對媒體說，「我相信烏克蘭人民會回答這個問題。不管是通過選舉還是公投，烏克蘭人民都必須有發言權。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0d428f32-3acf-34a1-911c-f5f06b55b380-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華盛頓、基輔和莫斯科朝著可能結束戰爭的協議艱難推進之際，領土問題成為了談判焦點。澤連斯基表示，美國探討了將頓巴斯稱為「自由經濟區」，而俄羅斯對其的定義則是「非軍事區」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美方正在探尋合適的形式，」 他說，「我們拭目以待吧。目前，我相信這很大程度上取決於我們的軍隊。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Floats Referendum Over Territory as US Pressure Mounts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93-%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%94%B1%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E9%A0%93%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E9%80%94-164830709.html",
