        },
        {
            "title": "歐盟達成協議將加強對外商投資審查力度 旨在保護本地區經濟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟就加強對外商直接投資審查達成初步協議，此舉旨在幫助保護當地經濟免受中美兩國政策影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四達成的協議將賦予歐盟更多權力，可對影響公共秩序和安全的外國投資進行審查和干預。該協議還將為審查此類投資設定歐盟基本標準，目前尚無此類標準。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們達成了一個平衡且相稱的框架，重點關注最敏感的技術和基礎設施，」丹麥工業、商業和金融事務部長Morten Bodskov表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟理事會與歐洲議會談判代表於周四上午敲定協議。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4570e7b9-108a-3aae-abde-1bcba1ef59dd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在歐洲應對川普關稅戰及中國對關鍵原物料實施限制之際，歐盟通過制定更嚴格的指導方針來保護本地區經濟。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月早些時候，歐盟發布了經濟安全綱領，強調必須確保外來投資不會使關鍵領域暴露於敵對所有權之下。綱領同時堅持要求，此類投資應為歐盟創造附加值，而非削弱歐盟的技術優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐盟披露新的經濟安全計畫 專注六大高風險領域以保持產業優勢</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Reaches Deal to Heighten Foreign Investment Screening</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%95%86%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-114218861.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-11 20:25:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "李嘉誠190億美元港口交易據悉因談判複雜而放慢速度",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 據知情人士透露，香港富豪李嘉誠試圖出售長江和記實業有限公司在全球各地數十個港口的交易放慢了速度，談判人員試圖理清阻礙達成協議的一系列問題。這些港口中有兩個位於具有戰略意義的巴拿馬運河。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士說，儘管談判仍在進行之中，但由於收購財團的結構等不確定因素，任何潛在交易的達成時間尚不明朗。他們還表示，由於各方在影響力和戰略上的分歧，導致談判已持續數月，仍看不到到明確的結束日期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們說，未決問題包括中國遠洋海運集團有限公司扮演何種角色。因討論未公開信息，知情人士要求匿名。這家中國最大的航運公司一直在洽談加入買家集團，與貝萊德旗下Global Infrastructure Partners，以及義大利億萬富豪詹路易吉·阿蓬特的Terminal Investment Ltd. (TiL) 一起進行收購。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-78cf0154-38c8-379f-8777-c44fb151d4ef-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"觀看：港口帝國來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fSI4pSBu7fOFDFA5rih0ag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/820cc56ee9a58abb246d8104ffd254f9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：港口帝國來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一位知情人士表示，包括阿蓬特家族在內的部分買家仍然堅持進行這筆交易，因為他們認為這筆交易對成長至關重要。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長和、TiL、中國遠洋海運集團各自的發言人均未回應尋求評論的請求。貝萊德的代表不予評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Li Ka-shing’s $19 Billion Ports Sale Slows Due to Complex Talks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Silla Brush.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0190%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%9B%A0%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C%E8%80%8C%E6%94%BE%E6%85%A2%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6-040156937.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-11 16:55:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國外交部長王毅將訪問阿聯酋、沙烏地、約旦 以拓展各領域交流合作",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國外交部長王毅將於近日訪問中東地區，包括沙烏地阿拉伯等國。中東對於<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:世界第二大經濟體;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/世界第二大經濟體\">世界第二大經濟體</a>中國的能源需求而言至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國外交部周四表示，王毅將於12月12日至16日訪問阿聯酋、沙烏地、約旦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外交部發言人郭嘉昆在例行記者會上表示，中國將藉此機會同三國「拓展各領域交流合作」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國約三分之二的原油進口自中東，也是沙烏地阿拉伯最大的原油買家之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年來，北京試圖在該地區發揮更大作用，成效不一。雖然中國在2023年促成伊朗與沙烏地實現外交緩和，但今年衝突導致該地區局勢不穩之際，中國未過於積極地介入。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2e8af5ce-d822-356c-8657-105d0522e3d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Top Diplomat to Visit Saudi Arabia on Middle East Trip</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Yongchang Chin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
